    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n<p>\n            Podstawy trapezu mają długości \\(a\\) i \\(b\\). Jego wysokość to \\(h\\), natomiast pole trapezu jest równe \\(P\\).\n        </p>\n<p>\n            Uzupełnij tabelę.\n        </p>\n<p>\n<small>W pierwszych trzech przykładach możesz sprawdzić pełne rozwiązanie</small>\n</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "flagged": true,
      "raw": "<table class=\"my_table_TC\">\n<tr>\n<th>\\(a\\)</th>\n<th>\\(b\\)</th>\n<th>\\(h\\)</th>\n<th>\\(P\\)</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\\(6\\)</td>\n<td>\\(3\\)</td>\n<td>\\(4\\)</td>\n<td><input class=\"table_input\" placeholder=\"wpisz\" type=\"text\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<details>\n<summary><small>rozwiązanie</small></summary>\n                        \\[\n                        P=\\frac{1}{2}(6+3)\\cdot 4=\\frac{1}{2}\\cdot 9\\cdot 4=18\n                        \\]\n                    </details>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\\(7\\)</td>\n<td>\\(2\\)</td>\n<td><input class=\"table_input\" placeholder=\"wpisz\" type=\"text\"/></td>\n<td>\\(13,5\\)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<details>\n<summary><small>rozwiązanie</small></summary>\n                        \\[\n                        \\begin{align}\n                        P&amp;=\\frac{1}{2}(a+b)\\cdot h\\\\\n                        13.5&amp;=\\frac{1}{2}(7+2)\\cdot h\\\\\n                        13.5&amp;=\\frac{1}{2}\\cdot 9\\cdot h\\\\\n                        \\frac{27}{2}&amp;=\\frac{9}{2}\\cdot h\\\\\n                        h&amp;=\\frac{27}{2}:\\frac{9}{2}\\\\\n                        h&amp;=\\frac{27}{2}\\cdot\\frac{2}{9}\\\\\n                        h&amp;=3\n                        \\end{align}\n                        \\]\n                    </details>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\\(14\\)</td>\n<td><input class=\"table_input\" placeholder=\"wpisz\" type=\"text\"/></td>\n<td>\\(9\\)</td>\n<td>\\(99\\)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<details>\n<summary><small>rozwiązanie</small></summary>\n                        \\[\n                        \\begin{align}\n                        P&amp;=\\frac{1}{2}(a+b)\\cdot h\\\\\n                        99&amp;=\\frac{1}{2}(14+b)\\cdot 9\\\\\n                        11&amp;=\\frac{1}{2}(14+b)\\\\\n                        22&amp;=14+b\\\\\n                        8&amp;=b\\\\\n                        b&amp;=8\n                        \\end{align}\n                        \\]\n                    </details>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\\(11\\)</td>\n<td>\\(9\\)</td>\n<td>\\(6\\)</td>\n<td><input class=\"table_input\" placeholder=\"wpisz\" type=\"text\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\\(11\\)</td>\n<td>\\(8\\)</td>\n<td><input class=\"table_input\" placeholder=\"wpisz\" type=\"text\"/></td>\n<td>\\(47.5\\)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><input class=\"table_input\" placeholder=\"wpisz\" type=\"text\"/></td>\n<td>\\(6\\)</td>\n<td>\\(5\\)</td>\n<td>\\(45\\)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\\(16\\)</td>\n<td>\\(12\\)</td>\n<td>\\(2\\)</td>\n<td><input class=\"table_input\" placeholder=\"wpisz\" type=\"text\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\\(13\\)</td>\n<td>\\(6\\)</td>\n<td><input class=\"table_input\" placeholder=\"wpisz\" type=\"text\"/></td>\n<td>\\(152\\)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\\(7\\)</td>\n<td><input class=\"table_input\" placeholder=\"wpisz\" type=\"text\"/></td>\n<td>\\(9\\)</td>\n<td>\\(54\\)</td>\n</tr>\n</table>",
